Package: SingleCellSignalR
Title: Cell Signalling Using Single Cell RNAseq Data Analysis
Version: 0.99.24
Authors@R: c(person("Simon", "Cabello-Aguilar", email = "simon.cabello-aguilar@inserm.fr", role = c("aut")), person("Jacques", "Colinge", email = "jacques.colinge@inserm.fr", role = c("cre","aut")))
Description: Allows single cell RNA seq data analysis, clustering, creates internal network and infers cell-cell interactions. It relies on the LRdb database and a KEGG-Reactome pathway database.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
